author: Associated Press
title: Ervin runs for 263 yards in San Jose State victory
text:
Photo: Marcio Jose Sanchez, Associated Press San Jose State’s Tyler Ervin bolts to a 71-yard touchdown in the first quarter of the Spartans’ home victory. Ervin finished with 263 yards on 36 carries. San Jose State’s Tyler Ervin bolts to a 71-yard touchdown in the...
Tyler Ervin rushed for 263 yards, including a 71-yard touchdown run on the second play from scrimmage, and host San Jose State beat New Mexico 31-21 on Saturday night.
